{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/vim/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"写几个字","author":"hengstchon"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"834e3e26-5e6e-5472-a4f1-cb86da5bbb58","excerpt":"Forward word movement: , , , . Backward word movement: , , , . “To the Character” movement: , , , , , . Paging: , , , . cursor jumping to screen parts…","html":"<p><strong>Forward word movement</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">w</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">W</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">e</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">E</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Backward word movement</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">b</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">B</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">ge</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">gE</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>“To the Character” movement</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">f</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">F</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">t</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">T</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">,</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">;</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Paging</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-f</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-b</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-u</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-d</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>cursor jumping to screen parts</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">H</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">M</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">L</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Top and Bottom of the buffer</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">gg</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">G</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Jumping to a particular line</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number&gt;G</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Easy regex searching</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">*</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">#</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Manual regular expression searching</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">/</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">?</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Jumping to Matching Braces</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">%</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Visual Mode</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">v</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">V</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-v</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">gv</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Navigate in help</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-]</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-T</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Increment or Decrement number</strong>: <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-A</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">CTRL-X</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Vim Plug 用法</strong></p>\n<p>在.vimrc 中写好插件后，用<code class=\"language-text\">:source ~/.vimrc</code>(在当前文件中可用<code class=\"language-text\">:so %</code>) 更新。然后<code class=\"language-text\">:PlugInstall</code>安装插件。</p>\n<p><strong>Vim’s Operator Commands</strong></p>\n<p><strong>c</strong>: Change</p>\n<p><strong>d</strong>: Delete</p>\n<p><strong>y</strong>: Yank into register</p>\n<p><strong>g~</strong>: Swap case</p>\n<p><strong>gu</strong>: Make lowercase</p>\n<p><strong>gU</strong>: Make uppercase</p>\n<p><strong>></strong>: Shift right</p>\n<p><strong>&#x3C;</strong>: Shift left</p>\n<p><strong>=</strong>: Autoindent</p>\n<p><strong>!</strong>: Filter {motion} lines through an external program</p>\n<ul>\n<li>count number of matches of a pattern: <code class=\"language-text\">:%s/pattern//gn</code></li>\n<li>jump to definition: <code class=\"language-text\">gd</code>, jump back: <code class=\"language-text\">gb</code></li>\n<li>show the same word under cursor: <code class=\"language-text\">*</code></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"","date":null},"fields":{"slug":"/vim/"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/vim/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/vim-plugins/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/vim-buffers/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}}}}